MAPPING.NAME: m_FCST_ITEM_SKU

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This transformation will update the target Table for New records
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: UPD_INSERT

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: THIS LOOKUP IS TO GET STYLE COLOR ,ATTRIBUTE , SIZE FOR MFB
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SLBA_ITEM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select ATTRIBUTION_CODE AS ATTRIBUTION_CODE, COLOR_CODE AS COLOR_CODE, SIZE_NUM AS SIZE_NUM, STYLE_NUM AS STYLE_NUM, TRIM(SAP_MATERIAL_NUM) AS SAP_MATERIAL_NUM, TRIM(SAP_GRID_VALUE) AS SAP_GRID_VALUE from slba_item where item_id in (select max (SI.item_id )FROM SLBA.SLBA_ITEM SI, style_master_1 SM, MTM_STYLE_GROUP A, HSF_BATCH.FCST_BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY BSH WHERE SI.STYLE_NUM= sm.style_num AND SI.DIVISION_GROUP = SM.DIVISION_GROUP AND nvl(TRIM(SI.COMPANY_CODE),'--') = nvl(TRIM(SM.COMPANY_CODE),'--') and trim(upper(sm.business_seg_desc)) = trim(upper(bsh.business_seg_desc)) and trim(upper(sm.sbu_desc)) = trim(upper(bsh.strategic_business_unit_desc)) and sm.company_code not in ('CG', 'SG') and sm.style_group != 'UNMAPPED' and sm.business_seg_desc not in ('UNMAPPED', 'Discontinued Operations', 'DTC', 'Group / Other') AND A.STYLE_GROUP_DESC=SM.style_group and sm.sbu_desc not in ('UNMAPPED', 'Other') AND A.STYLE_GROUP_ID!=500000 AND SI.DIVISION_GROUP ='slsp' and trim(SI.sap_grid_value) is not null and trim(SI.sap_material_num) is not null group by sap_material_num, sap_grid_value)

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This lookup is used to get the data from ITEM and ITEM_XREF tables.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_ITEM_ITEM_XREF

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT ITEM.STYLE_NUM as STYLE_NUM, ITEM.X_SIZE as X_SIZE, ITEM.PACK_CODE as PACK_CODE, ITEM.SIZE_LINE as SIZE_LINE, ITEM.SIZE_POS as SIZE_POS, ITEM_XREF.SLBA_ITEM_ITEM_ID as SLBA_ITEM_ITEM_ID FROM ITEM ITEM, ITEM_XREF ITEM_XREF WHERE ITEM.ITEM_ID=ITEM_XREF.ITEM_ITEM_ID AND ITEM.STYLE_NUM NOT LIKE 'UNMAP%'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Source Qualifier fetches data from style_master_1 table
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_STYLE_MASTER_1

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select SM.SELLING_STYLE AS SELLING_STYLE, SM.STYLE_GROUP, SM.STYLE_NUM AS STYLE_NUM, A.STYLE_GROUP_ID, SM.DIVISION_GROUP, SM.COMPANY_CODE, BSH.BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID from style_master_1 SM,MTM_STYLE_GROUP A,HSF_BATCH.FCST_BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY BSH WHERE sm.company_code not in ('CG', 'SG') and sm.style_group != 'UNMAPPED' and sm.business_seg_desc not in ('UNMAPPED', 'Discontinued Operations', 'DTC', 'Group / Other') AND A.STYLE_GROUP_DESC=SM.style_group and sm.sbu_desc not in ('UNMAPPED', 'Other') AND A.STYLE_GROUP_ID!=500000 and trim(upper(sm.business_seg_desc)) = trim(upper(bsh.business_seg_desc)) and trim(upper(sm.sbu_desc)) = trim(upper(bsh.strategic_business_unit_desc))

TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_FCST_ITEM_SKU

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT FCST_ITEM_SKU.FCST_SKU_KEY as FCST_SKU_KEY, FCST_ITEM_SKU.DIVISION_CODE as DIVISION_CODE, FCST_ITEM_SKU.DIVISION_GROUP as DIVISION_GROUP, FCST_ITEM_SKU.UPDATE_USERID as UPDATE_USERID, FCST_ITEM_SKU.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, FCST_ITEM_SKU.BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID as BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID FROM FCST_ITEM_SKU FCST_ITEM_SKU

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This Source Qualifier Fetches data from SLBA_ITEM ,FCST_BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY and MTM_STYLE_GROUP
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_SLBA_ITEM_BUS_SEG_HRCY

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT SI.ITEM_ID, SI.COLOR_CODE, SI.COMPANY_CODE, TRIM(SI.CUP_SIZE) AS CUP_SIZE, SI.DIVISION_CODE, SI.SIZE_NUM, SI.STYLE_NUM, SI.UPC_CODE, SI.DIVISION_GROUP, SI.X_SIZE, TRIM(SI.SAP_MATERIAL_NUM) AS SAP_MATERIAL_NUM, TRIM(SI.SAP_GRID_VALUE) AS SAP_GRID_VALUE, SI.SELLING_STYLE, SI.SIZE_LINE, SI.PACK_CODE, SI.SIZE_POSITION, SI.ITEM_STATUS, SI.PRODUCT_LINE_DESC, NVL(TRIM(SI.GTIN),0) AS GTIN, SI.SKU, SI.ATTRIBUTION_CODE, SI.SIZE_DESC, SI.SBU_DESC FROM SLBA.SLBA_ITEM SI WHERE NVL(SI.ITEM_STATUS,' ')<>'X'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This Transformation Will Update the existing records of Target table
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: UPD_UPDATE

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This Expression will Generate the SKU
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_SKU

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(I_COMPANY_CODE ='01'OR I_COMPANY_CODE ='03' OR I_COMPANY_CODE ='05' OR I_COMPANY_CODE ='BI' ,'B', IIF (DIVISION_GROUP='sli' AND I_COMPANY_CODE='20' OR I_COMPANY_CODE='PL' OR I_COMPANY_CODE='41' OR I_COMPANY_CODE='40' OR I_COMPANY_CODE='35','P','U'))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_SLI_COMPANY_CODE_PREFIX

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF( I_COMPANY_CODE='10' OR I_COMPANY_CODE='30' OR I_COMPANY_CODE='60' ,'H', IIF(I_COMPANY_CODE='21'OR I_COMPANY_CODE='20','L','U'))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_SLH_COMPANY_CODE_PREFIX
V_MFB_SKU

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(DIVISION_GROUP ='hbi' and DIVISION_CODE='DS' AND INSTR (UPPER(I_STYLE_GROUP),'FIN') >0 , I_SM_STYLE_NUM || '_' ||I_STYLE_GROUP , IIF(DIVISION_GROUP ='hbi' and DIVISION_CODE='DS' AND INSTR (UPPER(I_STYLE_GROUP),'FIN') =0 , I_SM_STYLE_NUM||'_' || I_STYLE_GROUP,'UNMAPPED' ))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_HBI_SKU

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(SUBSTR(DIVISION_GROUP,1,3)='dba' AND DIVISION_CODE='DB' , I_STYLE_NUM || '_' || RTRIM(LTRIM(SUBSTR(I_COLOR_CODE,1,4))) || '_' || SUBSTR(I_SIZE_NUM,1,3) || IIF(NOT ISNULL(LTRIM(RTRIM(I_CUP_SIZE))),'_' || LTRIM(RTRIM(I_CUP_SIZE)),NULL),'')
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_DB_SKU

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
IIF( NOT ISNULL (V_SKU_SBU),V_SKU_SBU, IIF( SUBSTR(DIVISION_GROUP,1,3)='dba' AND DIVISION_CODE='DB', V_DB_SKU, DECODE (DIVISION_GROUP,'slu',IIF(NOT ISNULL(I_SLBA_ITEM_ITEM_ID),RPAD(LTRIM(RTRIM(I_STYLE_NUM1)),6,' ') || '_' || LTRIM(RTRIM(I_X_SIZE1)) || '_' || LTRIM(RTRIM(I_PACK_CODE1)) || '_' || LTRIM(RTRIM(I_SIZE_LINE1)) || LTRIM(RTRIM(I_SIZE_POS)), 'UNMAPPED'),
'sls', IIF( I_PRODUCT_LINE_DESC <> 'IRREGULAR' AND I_GTIN <> '000000000000' , LTRIM(RTRIM(I_SM_SELLING_STYLE)) || '_' || LTRIM(RTRIM(I_UPC_CODE)) ||'_' || to_char(I_STYLE_GROUP_ID),'UNMAPPED') ,
'sli',V_SLI_COMPANY_CODE_PREFIX || '_' || SUBSTR(I_STYLE_NUM,1,4) ||'_' || SUBSTR(I_COLOR_CODE,1,3) || '_' || LTRIM(RTRIM(I_SIZE_NUM)) || IIF(NOT ISNULL(LTRIM(RTRIM(I_CUP_SIZE))), '_' || LTRIM(RTRIM(I_CUP_SIZE)) , NULL ),
'slh',V_SLH_COMPANY_CODE_PREFIX || '_' || SUBSTR(I_STYLE_NUM, 1, 5) || '_' || SUBSTR(I_COLOR_CODE, 1, 3) || '_' || SUBSTR(I_SIZE_NUM, 1,2),
'mex', I_STYLE_NUM || '_' || SUBSTR(I_COLOR_CODE,1,3) || '_' || SUBSTR(I_SIZE_NUM,1,3),
'slca', I_STYLE_NUM || '_' || SUBSTR(I_COLOR_CODE,1,3) || '_' || SUBSTR(I_SIZE_NUM,1,3) || IIF(NOT ISNULL(LTRIM(RTRIM(I_CUP_SIZE))),'_' ||LTRIM(RTRIM( I_CUP_SIZE)) , NULL ),
'mfb', V_MFB_SKU,
'slsp', I_STYLE_NUM || '_' || RTRIM(LTRIM(SUBSTR(I_COLOR_CODE,1,4))) || '_' ||I_ATTRIBUTION_CODE || '_' || SUBSTR(I_SIZE_NUM,1,3),
'sld', I_STYLE_NUM || '_' || I_COLOR_CODE ||IIF(NOT ISNULL(LTRIM(RTRIM(I_SIZE_DESC))), '_' ||I_SIZE_DESC,''),
'hbi', V_HBI_SKU,
'S4',V_S4_SKU,
'UNMAPPED'
)))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: O_FCST_SKU_KEY

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
--IIF(DIVISION_GROUP <> 'slsp','Y', --IIF((DIVISION_GROUP = 'slsp' AND NOT ISNULL(I_SAP_MATERIAL_NUM)),'Y','N') --)
IIF(DIVISION_GROUP = 'slsp' and (NOT ISNULL(I_SAP_MATERIAL_NUM) or I_SAP_MATERIAL_NUM <> '') and not isnull(I_LKP_GRID_VALUE) ,'Y','N')
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_FLAG
